Installation requirements:
  - [mininum] Ruby 2.0.0p648
  - gem sinatra
  - gem httparty
  - port 8080 open

To install the gems:
  sudo gem install sinatra
  sudo gem install httparty

Routes available:
  - get '/orders' -> returns a stringified version of the current orders
  - post '/orders/:tablet_id' -> Adds an order to the list and notify the display, returns a status + the average time

To run the server:
  ruby [Eable-Core location]/lib/bin/server.rb
